text.tspan: All you need is the 48px size. Other sizes are nice, but not required.
See https://hig.kde.org/style/icons/ for icon design advice
Ikona will add classes to objects of these colours so they respect the system colour palette
This template is best used in Inkscape. Refrain from touching the Baseplates group, as Ikona uses information stored in it to crop your icon.
